CS 4500: Software Development: Spring 2010
==========================================

[Testing Grammars]
Create your grammer in a .grm file.
Create your tests in a .txt file.
Run:
    cat <grammar> | python test_grammar.py -i <tests>

    or

    python test_grammar.py <grammar> <tests>

For an example, see json_base.grm and json_base_tests.txt
